warning[L0012]: This `if`/`else if` chain dispatches on one value вҖ” a `when` would be checked for exhaustiveness.
  в”Ӯ
  в”ңв”Җрңұ¶ help: rewrite as `when <subject> is <pattern> { вҖҰ } вҖҰ` so the compiler verifies every case is handled (open types like `int` still need an `else`).
  в”Ӯ
